title: 'This is perfect!'
body: Usually ordering oversized clothes means either they won't fit right in some way or they'll make it shapelessly huge. Almost funny looking? Feels like mockery.  But this is perfect Material is great Stitch is great Fitting is amazing Packaging is good Colours available are good and same as shown in product images above.  Price (being 4XL) was still 600 which was great, as usually we see prices go on increasing with bigger size.  Looks overall are fab! So just pick your favourite colour and go for it!  9/10 (Because for slimmer sizes this is a TADDD BIT pricey. Hehe)
